@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative One

autonumber

actor "Human Resources\nManager" as GRH
participant ":System" as System

activate GRH

    GRH -> System : asks to create a new task
    activate System

        System --> GRH : requests data (i.e. designation, detailed task\ndescription, duration, deadline)
    deactivate System

    GRH -> System : types requested data
    activate System

        System --> GRH : shows task category list and asks to select one
    deactivate System

    GRH -> System : selects a task category
    activate System

        System --> GRH : shows the list of task requirements and asks\nyou to select all the necessary ones
    deactivate System

    GRH -> System : selects the requirements for the task
    activate System

        System --> GRH : shows all data and requests confirmation
    deactivate System

    GRH -> System : confirms data
    activate System

        System --> GRH : show the team recommendation
    deactivate System

    GRH -> System : accepts team recommendation
    activate System

        System --> GRH : displays operation success
    deactivate System

@enduml